summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the conduct of vehicle operators upon the occurrence of an accident; amending Sections 12A.28.120 and 12A.28.160 of the Seattle Criminal Code (Ordinance 102843), adding a new section thereto designated Section 12A.28.165, and repealing as of the effective date of said Code Sections 21.52.100 and 21.52.110 of the Traffic Code (Ordinance 91910).
